      <summary>
        <versionCode>07</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2025-07-15</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Reported to House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2025-09-03T15:37:57Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Securities Research Modernization Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill allows a securities broker or dealer to publish or distribute a research report on a proposed public offering by any issuer without it being considered an offer to sell securities for purposes of registration requirements. Currently, only reports published or distributed regarding a proposed public offering by an emerging growth company fall under this exception.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
